*   skeleton (NodePath): Default: NodePath("").
*   texture (Texture2D)
*   texture_offset (Vector2): Default: Vector2(0, 0).
*   texture_rotation (float): Default: 0.0.
*   texture_scale (Vector2): Default: Vector2(1, 1).
*   uv (PackedVector2Array): Default: PackedVector2Array().
*   vertex_colors (PackedColorArray): Default: PackedColorArray().
